    " Deep learning models are sensitive to data quality.",
    "Noisy or mislabeled data can negatively impact model performance.",
    " Deep learning models can struggle with imbalanced datasets where certain classes have much fewer examples than others.",
    "Special techniques are needed to handle this issue effectively.",
    " It is time-consuming process to find right hyperparameters for deep learning models."
